{"tid":1366384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保護元朗, 增加對香港既認識","createTime":"2019-07-26T02:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T12:45:32.000Z","uid":55177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f87116587aa54dcf91586e829fb536f91345c4","tid":1366384,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"元朗作為香港其中一個最有歷史同特色文化既區, 香港人點可以對佢一D認識都冇<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於近日元朗比較動盪, 原先我係唔鼓勵大家係呢個時候去元朗參觀<br />\n<br />\n但係警察尋日出左反對通知書禁止遊行, <br />\n大家終於可以安安穩穩咁去元朗享受一日難得既週未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議大家去到元朗可以去周圍行下, 參觀下當地既建築, 感受下當地既歷史, <br />\n尤其要多d同本地居民溝通, 深入咁了解該區既特色同文化<br />\n<br />\n有興趣係附近行山, 睇下牛既朋友要記得帶齊食水食物之類, 同埋相應既行山, 燒烤, 野炊既裝備<br />\n<br />\n有興趣攀石同踩單車既朋友記得要戴頭盔, <br />\n至於會燒烤生火既朋友記得戴口罩同眼罩避免吸入太多灰同炭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝大家可以好好咁係元朗享受一個平靜既週末<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d39c31ed97bef5c594d9fa915522358eec04ed","tid":1366384,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:57:14.000Z","msg":"咁多位朋友要去就聽日去啦, 下個週末就唔知會唔會咁好彩禁止遊行,<br />\n<br />\n如果下個星期元朗有遊行大家可能就錯過左難得既機會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ecfa049bb4c0104d3b0601a9ee0b0c97764954e","tid":1366384,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ts7gMRs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTs7gMRs.jpg&h=6046cfb7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}